en:
“First of all, you need to secure your position and build your base of operation, secure the outcome of the resource, because war requires much, You must control your force because the army is not just soldiers who fight, but also peasants who support them with provision. It’s vital to control your personnel,  one could be a soldier or peasant - depending on the situation, peasants could be assigned for gathering resources and provisions for the army. And soldiers, you know what soldiers do lad.”

Build a foraging tent and assign a worker to it, choose the resource you want to gather;
Build a foraging tent and assign a worker to it;
Hire at least 3-4 more NPC, turn them into soldiers, equip and return them to me.

th:
“首先你要找到一个安全的地点建设你的基地，确保资源的获取，战争会消耗很多. 你必须管理好你的军队，因为军队不仅仅是打仗的士兵，还有用供给支持他们的农民。管理你的人至关重要，一个人根据情况即可以是士兵，也可以是农民. 农民可以被指派为军队收集资源和供给。而士兵，你应该很清楚是做什么的,小伙子”

建造一个采集营，并为其分配一名工人，选择你想收集的资源;
建造一个采集营，并为其分配一名工人;
再雇佣至少3-4个NPC，把他们变成士兵，装备好后把他们交给我

